name: Rin Tohsaka (Fate: Stay Night) | Character LoRA - SemestaAI
description:
so yesterday, when i'm searching for ideas, i stumbled upon a user with "RinTohsakaSimp" as his UserID. all his post is about lewding over Rin 😆. (he's not civitai user, i found it on other site.)

i myself like Rin, if i had to make a character tierlist, i will place her in S Tier. it's just has been over 4 years since i watch fate. so i'm not thinking about making her LoRA until yesterday.

and that's why today i decided to make this RinTohsaka LoRA. i wonder what's his reaction when see this post 😄.

anyway, here's some prompt suggestion:

(RinTohsaka), black hair, black skirt, red sweater, twintails,

it's just an examples, you can tweak it as you need.

__________

Visit My Patreon if you want to support me. I'm also accepting LoRA Commissions & Requests.
